sections.text: Conflicts of interest6-534.Conflicts of interestA director, committee member, officer, agent or employee of the credit union shall not in any manner participate, directly or indirectly, in the deliberation or the determination of any question affecting that person's pecuniary or other personal interest or the pecuniary interest of any organization, other than the credit union, in which the person is directly or indirectly interested.
